      "updated": 1773832324320,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If we know IP address of other A we can do peer to peer connection. But this is not scalable if there are many users.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 18,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If we know IP address of other A we can do peer to peer connection. But this is not scalable if there are many users.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B5p9SKv5ku0DF8ZdRoaod",
