      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773832324320,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "But we have thousands of chat server, some user would be connected to one server. Using user mapping service we can identify which\nuser would be connected to which server. This is connected from websockets but few operation requires http for example login.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 68,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "But we have thousands of chat server, some user would be connected to one server. Using user mapping service we can identify which\nuser would be connected to which server. This is connected from websockets but few operation requires http for example login.\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
